    "description": "Ghosted neon energy fields with hexagonal lattice structures: zone borders emit cyberpunk-colored phantom energy that spirals inward through ping-pong feedback, accumulating into spectral hex grids and octahedral interference patterns; bass triggers shockwave distortions, mids shift the hex lattice topology, treble injects glitch sparks with scanline interference",
